  "text": "The working point concept for the volume domain has been explained before [CITATION_1] . Briefly, the position of point P ( Fig. 1) is reflected by the coordinates {EDVi,ESVi}. The prevailing value of EF can be visualized in the VRG [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , as further explained in the Supplement. This exercise adds information to the metric EF, and in fact demonstrates that the EFC (or indexed EFCi when BSA is applied) is the inseparable partner of EF.",
